reviewText: I hate it because I'm an idiot and didn't fully read the title of this item. When I received this item I soon discovered I am unable to watch this. So now I'm either stuck with a series I cannot watch or I'll give it to Goodwill or the dump.
The product is OK and as advertised.  Nevertheless, when it said that could played all over the world I expected to have other spoken languages, it is only in English.
